      "parameters": {
        "content": "🚀 AI Social Media Automation Workflow\n\nThis workflow automates end-to-end content creation and publishing:\n\n1. Input:\n- Topic is fetched dynamically from Google Sheets\n\n2. Content Generation:\n- Google Gemini generates platform-specific captions, hashtags, CTA, and image prompt\n- Output is parsed and structured via Code node\n\n3. Media Generation:\n- Leonardo AI generates image using prompt",
