    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "\n4. Platform Routing:\n- Conditional IF nodes route content to:\n  • Instagram (image-based)\n  • Facebook (image post)\n  • LinkedIn (professional post)\n  • YouTube (video upload)\n\n5. Publishing:\n- Posts are automatically published using platform APIs\n- Supports multi-platform execution in parallel\n\n6. Data Logging:\n- All generated content stored in Google Sheets\n- Posting status tracked (Posted / Not Posted)",
        "height": 336,
        "width": 624
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
