      "name": "Sticky Note2"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "7. Error Handling:\n- Fail-safe IF condition checks final merged output\n- If success → logs as \"Posted\"\n- If failure → logs as \"Not Posted\"\n\n8. Scalability:\n- Modular design allows adding more platforms or approval steps\n- Can be extended with scheduling or human-in-loop review\n\n🎯 Outcome:\nFully automated AI-powered content pipeline from idea → generation → publishing → logging",
